	description="Professional mobile computer service in DFW. Certified technicians, 90-day warranty, 500+ repairs. We come to you 7 days/week. Call (469) 430-8607"
	keywords="about GadgetFix, mobile computer service experts Dallas, Fort Worth computer service, certified technicians DFW, professional computer service, service company Dallas"
