					<p>Every service comes with a comprehensive 90-day guarantee because we stand behind our work. Our commitment is simple: provide the highest quality computer service with the convenience of coming directly to you, whether you're at home, work, or anywhere else in the DFW Metroplex.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="story-image animate-on-scroll">
					<img 
						src="/images/jeshoots-com-sMKUYIasyDM-unsplash.jpg" 
						alt="Expert technicians at work repairing electronic devices"
						loading="lazy"
						width="600"
						height="400"
					/>
